record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 106 AND H. RES. 610
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 106 AND H. RES. 610 -- (House of Representatives - October 15, 2007)

[Page: H11533]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that I be removed as a cosponsor from H. Res. 106 and H. Res. 610.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from Michigan?
